15_0	0.093958753	WEST PALM BEACH, Fla.
15_1	0.2251781	_ Hepatitis C.
15_2	0.088292487	Is this the disease that should scare the middle-age bejesus out of Baby Boomers for their dumb indiscretions 25 years ago?
